article_title: Cat nap: Darrell Issa purr-fectly demonstrates Obamacare call center experience [pic] – twitchy.com
article_text:
Much of the focus has been on the HealthCare.gov fail, but the Obamacare sign-up experience by phone has also been less than optimal, to say the least.

Rep. Darrell Issa described it with this Buzzfeed-ish headline:

8 cats who couldn't signup for #healthcare using 1-800 #ObamaCare >> http://t.co/RsYIeLCo73 #listicle — Darrell Issa (@DarrellIssa) October 23, 2013

Here’s number eight:

Purr-fect.
